title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of restaurants, with a total of 12 data points.
Overall Number of restaurants has increased over the Year.
Number of restaurants is roughly constant from 2007 to 2009, gradually increasing from 2009 to 2015, and lastly roughly constant from 2015 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2011 and 2012.
Max Number of restaurants about 5303.0 was recorded at Year 2018
Min Number of restaurants about 3208.0 was recorded at Year 2007
